	---------------------------------------------
	Changes from version 3.0.2 to version 3.1.0
	---------------------------------------------

************
*   In R
************
- function MCMC takes extra argument miss.loc for status of doubly missing genotypes

- function Planarproj removed

- added packages maps and mapproj to DEPENDS field in DESCRIPTION file

- in functiob MCMC changed default freq. model to uncorrelated	

	
******************
*   In Fortran
******************
- Subroutine mcmcgld takes extra argument missloc for status of doubly missing genotypes


- Subroutine udyNA takes extra argument missloc for status of doubly missing genotypes	
	


